                {
                  "id": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3rf5m19f/manifest/annotation/p2",
                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>all those who complained that they did not<lb/> receive the “Occidents” regularly,\n                that they never<lb/> ordered them, that they gave notice for a<lb/> discontinuation\n                &amp;c &amp;c. &amp; I have deemed it<lb/> to be your benefit to comply with your\n                request<lb/> &amp; took all I could get from the parties.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">You have <persName>Mr Mayblum</persName> down for 2 years;<lb/> he\n                says that he recd the “Occident” in the capacity<lb/> of <placeName>South\n                    Carolina</placeName> of Post Master &amp; as such did<lb/> not think himself\n                liable for any subscription &amp;c<lb/> therefore I have compromised it for\n                $3.00</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">$5.00 is all I could collect from <persName>H\n                Neustadter</persName>;<lb/> says that he did not wish the Occid for<lb/> some time;\n                he <hi rend=\"underline\">wishes to stop his subscription</hi><lb/> The same remark is\n                applicable to <persName>D. Stern</persName></p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\"><persName>Mr Saml Hart</persName> wishes all the back<lb/> Nos since\n                the weekly has been commenced</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\"><persName>Hamburger Bros</persName> think they cannot owe<lb/> you\n                $15.00, still if you were sure they will<lb/> pay the Balance of $5.00</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">$7.50 was the most I could draw from <persName>Scholle<lb/>\n                    Bros</persName>; they wish the “Occident” no more.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\"><persName>H. W. Stern</persName> makes the reason for paying<lb/>\n                less, not receiving it &amp; <add>?</add>; he also wishes to<lb/> discontinue his\n                subscription</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\"><persName>Mr S. T. Meyer</persName>, whom you have on the<lb/> list\n                resides now at <placeName>New York</placeName>; <persName>Mr Aaron<lb/>\n                    Jacobs</persName> there can tell you where he can be<lb/> found. <persName>Jules\n                    Cerf</persName> makes also the excuse</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3rf5m19f/canvas/p2"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
