          "annotations": [
            {
              "id": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3rf5m19f/canvas/p3/annopage",
              "type": "AnnotationPage",
              "items": [
                {
                  "id": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3rf5m19f/manifest/annotation/p3",
                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>not having subscribed &amp; <add>?</add> he wishes to dis-<lb/>-continue his\n                subscription, you will observe<lb/> that I also settled with him.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Since you gave me authority to settle<lb/> with the parties who made\n                excuses &amp; complaints<lb/> to escape payments, I have used it, &amp;<lb/> with my\n                most active endeavors in your<lb/> behalf have I worked to make these\n                collections,<lb/> &amp; I trust you will approve of my work.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I would beg leave to suggest to you to<lb/> stop always the\n                subscription when desired,<lb/> as you cannot afford to supply people<lb/> with\n                papers without their wishes &amp; payments.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Please do not forget to acknowledge<lb/> in your next issue all the\n                various<lb/> payments as collected; as I have not given<lb/> any receipts, save in a\n                single instance.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Please accept the following new<lb/> subscribers I got:\n                        <persName><hi rend=\"underline\">Lewis Cohn</hi></persName>, <placeName>San\n                    Francisco</placeName><lb/>\n                <persName>J. A. <hi rend=\"underline\">Bruner</hi></persName>, <placeName>San\n                    Francisco</placeName>, (the latter<lb/> gentleman has paid one year's\n                subscription<lb/> in advance, which you will observe amongst<lb/> the list of\n                collections) <persName><hi rend=\"underline\">Regensburger</hi><lb/>\n                    <hi rend=\"underline\">&amp; Stern</hi></persName>\n                <placeName>San Francisco</placeName>, whose subscription<lb/> is in place of\n                    <persName>D Stern</persName> (discontinued)</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\"><persName>Mr Alexander Mayer</persName> who arrived<lb/> here in\n                safety from <placeName>Phil</placeName> requests me to<lb/> state that he has sold\n                all the bibles save<lb/> one. <persName>Mr Jacob Bloomingdale</persName> whom</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3rf5m19f/canvas/p3"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
