              "items": [
                {
                  "id": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3rf5m19f/manifest/annotation/p4",
                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>you have on the list lives now in<lb/>\n                <placeName>Germany</placeName> think <placeName>Frankfort</placeName>. I see that\n                you have<lb/>\n                <persName>Haas</persName> &amp; <persName>Rosenfeld</persName> on the list for\n                $15.00, which<lb/> is doubtful that I will be able to collect<lb/> as on their last\n                payment they requested<lb/> a discontinuance, of which I wrote you<lb/> at the time.\n                    <persName>Raphael Schoyer</persName> is<lb/> not in the city, he left for\n                    <placeName>Japan</placeName>.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\"><persName>S. Fleishhacker</persName> resides at\n                    <placeName>Placerville</placeName><lb/> &amp; I hope you will not send him<lb/>\n                the “Occident” as you can never ex-<lb/>-pect a cent from him, being too fond<lb/>\n                of whiskey &amp; rum. <persName>Hess</persName> lives in <placeName>N\n                    York</placeName>.<lb/> where <persName>Cha-Simon</persName> is I cannot\n                tell,<lb/> you better therefore discontinue sending<lb/> the “Occid” to him. From\n                    <persName>F. M.<lb/> Reinhart</persName> I cannot collect anything; he<lb/>\n                lives here now &amp; am well acquainted<lb/> with him. <persName>Aaron\n                    Rosenheim</persName> does not<lb/> live anymore at\n                <placeName>Nevada</placeName>, he resides<lb/> here now; I think his Brother lives\n                there<lb/> yet. You are wrong in believing <del>then</del><lb/>\n                <persName>Aaron Rosenheim</persName> rich.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I have made those collections<lb/> all myself; time did not allow\n                me<lb/> to call on every one as yet, but shall<lb/> do so as soon as I shall have\n                some</p>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3rf5m19f/canvas/p4"
                }
              ]
